    description: 'Understand the Federal Geodetic Control Subcommittee specifications for geodetic leveling, the Geospatial Positioning Accuracy Standards (GPAS), and the US National Map Accuracy Standards. These standards define accuracy classifications, tolerances, and testing procedures that appear on the FS exam.',
    estimatedMinutes: 20,
